%h2#molinillo Using Molinillo for Dependency Resolution

.contents
  .bullet
    .description
      %p
        Bundler's dependency resolver is now powered by Molinillo, the CocoaPods
        dependency resolution algorithm sponsored by Stripethat is fully
        documented, tested, and built for use across different dependency
        managers built in Ruby.
        = link_to 'Molinillo', 'https://github.com/CocoaPods/Molinillo'

%h2#path-gemspec-detection Improved gemspec detection

.contents
  .bullet
    .description
      %p
        Directories are now searched resursively for gemspecs, with specs found
        closer to the root being preferred.

%h2#other-changes Other changes

.contents
  .bullet
    .description
      Bundler 1.9 also includes:
      %ul
        %li improved vendoring of <code>thor</code> that will make conflicts less common
        %li fixed gemspecs generated by <code>bundle gem</code> from a pre-release bundler version
        %li <code>bundle which</code> will no longer be confused by directories
      = link_to 'Full 1.9 changelog', 'https://github.com/bundler/bundler/blob/1-9-stable/CHANGELOG.md'
